<title>USA: Performance Tech sets 3-for-2 shr split.</title>
<headline>Performance Tech sets 3-for-2 shr split.</headline>
<dateline>ROCHESTER, N.Y. 1997-07-31</dateline>
<text>
<p>Performance Technologies Inc on Thursday set a three-for-two split of the company's common stock.</p>
<p>Company stockholders will receive one additional share for each two shares owned as of the record date, August 29, the company said.</p>
<p>The split will result in about 7.2 million common shares outstanding, the company said.</p>
<p>The stock split will be paid as a 50-percent stock dividend on September 15, the company said.</p>
